name: AIroticArt's Penis Model (LoRA)
description:
Update 4/2/23: For more examples, we used this LoRA to help create the penises in our art, The Beauty of Couples, Collection #14.

This is a LoRA version of our Penis Model. It was extracted from the regular v1.0 of that model (we don't think it is possible to extract LoRAs from inpainting models). This LoRA still does best as an "inpainting model," when used in inpainting mode to fix penis anatomy or add detail, with the same trigger words as the main model.

Note: the sample images were generated with a different model, and then the penis was inpainted with this LoRA to enhance. The metadata in the images is for the inpainting pass only.

modelVersions.name: v1.0 LoRA
modelVersions.description: Extracted from the v1.0 model. Best used in inpainting.
